sequenceDiagram
  participant Client
  participant API
  participant Orchestrator
  participant Tool
  participant Store
  Client->>API: /api/v1/agents/ask
  API->>Orchestrator: route(question)
  Orchestrator->>Tool: selected tool call
  Tool->>Store: retrieve data/context
  Store-->>Tool: context/data
  Tool-->>Orchestrator: result
  Orchestrator-->>API: response + trace
  API-->>Client: JSON
